g++ audiochk.cpp  -I"../../irrKlang-64bit-1.6.0/include" -L"/usr/lib" ../../irrKlang-64bit-1.6.0/bin/linux-gcc-64/libIrrKlang.so -pthread


within the first two quotation marks, write the path to the include directory 
in the last two marks write the path to libIrrKlang.so

you should be able to find the both of them inside your irrklang directory. then do pwd and copy path
